Interface CalculatorAdvancedOperations

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CalculatorBasicOperations
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface CalculatorAdvancedOperations
extends CalculatorBasicOperations
    Interface for trigonometric functions sine, cosine, tangent and hyperbolic functions hyperbolic sine, hyperbolic cosine and hyperbolic tangent. Uses numbers of the type double.
